text: Sarah Wesam Aboufasha, better known by her pseudonym; Sarah Fasha (Arabic: سارة فاشا) (born 1991) is an Egyptian-American comedic YouTube personality, vlogger, motivational speaker, and winner of Miss Egypt in the Queen of the Universe Pageant 2013. She is known mostly for her success in Egypt after winning her pageant title in the United States. She was born in Los Angeles, California. ==References== Category:American Internet celebrities Category:American movie actors Category:Living people Category:Models from Los Angeles Category:1991 births Category:American television actors Category:Egyptian actors
